td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of the third indent of Article 2(4)(b) of Council Directive 2003/96/EC of 27 October 2003 restructuring the Community framework for the taxation of energy products and electricity (
OJ 2003 L 283, p. 51
).

Article 2(1) of that directive defines energy products, drawing up a list of products falling within the Combined Nomenclature codes set out in Annex I to Council Regulation (EEC) No 2658/87 of 23 July 1987 on the tariff and statistical nomenclature and on the Common Customs Tariff (
OJ 1987 L 256, p. 1
). Article 2(2) of that directive states that it also applies to electricity falling within code 2716 of that nomenclature.
